Suitable numbers are available in the Yar's Revenge source code (look near the bottom, starting at line #2685).  Note that they are upside down, which is typical of graphics assets in Atari 2600 games (makes them easier to feed into the TIA during hblank).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3664">clueless</a> — Wed Nov 24, 2010 6:25 am</p><hr />
